    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey @yudawp, it doesn't seem like your problem is related to this issue. You can find the documentation for [`connectSortBy` on the Algolia website](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/sort-by/js/#connector). Note that connectors are available on the `instantsearch.connectors` object, not `instantsearch.widgets`.\r\n\r\nIf this doesn't help, please [create another issue](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/new/choose) so that we don't lose the focus of this original thread.",
